arn.description: The ARN assigned by AWS for this group.

name.description: The group's name. The name must consist of upper and lowercase alphanumeric characters with no spaces. You can also include any of the following characters: `=,.@-_.`. Group names are not distinguished by case. For example, you cannot create groups named both "ADMINS" and "admins".
